        "timestamp": "2018-01-05 06:24:12.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 6:\n\n> http://jenkins.onap.info/job/oom-cd/1013/console\n\nMichael, there should be option to trigger jenkins job when there is a new review. And the job can vote accordingly to success or failure.",
        "patchset_number": 6
      },
      {
        "id": "2901b429264f236b2573cadf0761dfd15906a318",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 137,
          "name": "Alexis de Talhouet",
